					<p>ShoutBox was created by two Developers from Edmonton, Alberta who sought out a way to make tweeting from the desktop a more enjoyable experience. </p>
					<a class="special first_button" target="_blank" href="http://www.ualberta.ca/~hsingh3/">Harpreet Singh</a>
					<a class="special" target="_blank" href="http://www.arjunkalburgi.com/">Arjun Kalburgi</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

